dismissalText.commentary: Ricky Ponting c Muralidaran b Dharmasena 56 (71b 1x4 0x6 92m) SR: 78.87

notes: PA de Silva 50 in 87 mins off 76 balls
WPUJC Vaas batted with a runner for one ball before being dismissed.

During change of innings, the match referee announced that a 3 by de Silva should have been a 4. The innings was thus increased from 9-254 to 9-255 and de Silva's, Kasprowicz's, and the FoW figures were changed accordingly.
MA Taylor run out by direct hit from Muralitharan at deep mid-on
SG Law dropped on 1 by Ranatunga
Winning shot was a 4 by Bevan off the 3rd last ball of the match
